+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0+
+/*
+ * Board file for the LORIX One (256MB) platform
+ * Based on the the SAMA5D4 Xplained Ultra board file
+ * Copyright (C) 2014 Atmel
+ *		      Bo Shen <voice.shen@atmel.com>
